name: Bryan Albanaque
description: I am an honest, loyal (sometimes to a fault), fun-loving, intelligent, deep thinking, giving person. I am also passionate about my career, personal goals and seeing my dreams come true. I am also a believer in Karma and “what is meant to be will be”. There is a romantic in me that enjoys being spontaneous and doing the little things that matter. For fun I enjoy: traveling, performing arts, cooking, feature films and art galleries. Having a glass of wine, watching a sunset, and spending time with friends & family are all great too. I stay in great shape with a variety of activities. Lastly, I am genuine and mean what I say. There is no game playing here.
